---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white pt-12 pb-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1">
        <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">
          News<span class="text-blue-500">Portal</span>.
        </a>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 text-sm">
          Platform berita terdepan yang menyajikan informasi terkini, akurat, dan terpercaya dari berbagai sumber.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-200">Kategori</h3>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
          <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Nasional</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Internasional</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Teknologi</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Olahraga</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-200">Perusahaan</h3>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
          <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Tentang Kami</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Redaksi</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Karir</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Kontak</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-200">Langganan</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 text-sm">Dapatkan berita terbaru langsung di inbox Anda.</p>
        <form class="mt-4">
          <div class="flex">
            <input type="email" placeholder="Email Anda" class="px-4 py-2 w-full rounded-l-lg text-gray-900 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" />
            <button class="bg-blue-600 px-4 py-2 rounded-r-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
              Subscribe
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-gray-800 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">&copy; {currentYear} NewsPortal. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
